abstract: Ariya Jutanugarn takes third-round lead at Yokohama Tire LPGA Classic golf tournament in Prattville, Ala; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Ariya Jutanugarn of Thailand shot a nine-under-par 63, reeling off eight birdies on the back nine, to surge to a three-stroke lead.

headline.main: Thai Player Opens Lead With a Torrid Back 9
